commit.message:
SignatureTest: Test PKCS8 private key

PKCS8 format is supported as well, togheter with PKCS1 format

PdfFilter: Completely moved the class to private folder

This further reduces the public API surface. PdfFilter was
already an implementation detail and not exposed in any header,
and the user is not supposed to be able to inherit/create
filters directly. This turned to be necessary as some linkers
may not like classes with private constructors that are not used
in any place. It actually caused undefined error with GNU ld
linked binaries in some circumstances, for non obvious reason
as the symbols were never used externally

PdfFontConfigWrapper: Added some missing directives to __APPLE__ and __ANDROID__ fallback configurations

In some circumstances a "Fontconfig error: No writable cache directories" message was issued
build-mac.yml: Try fix missing noticing of HOMEBREW_NO_INSTALLED_DEPENDENTS_CHECK setting

[UPD] Try to speed up dependencies install with HOMEBREW_NO_INSTALLED_DEPENDENTS_CHECK

See https://docs.brew.sh/Manpage#install-options-formulacask-
[UPD] Try to advance github workflow build-mac.yml from macos-11 to macos-12 to hopefully fix dependencies install

StreamDevice: Remove final from most classes

Rationale: Allowing inheritance allows to create stateful standalone instances
[FIX] Silence warning on use of typeid(*ptr) in clang
PdfSigner: Fixed warning trying to silence another warning...
PdfSigningContext: Fixed wrong class doc
PdfImage: Return inline width and height
StandardStreamDevice: Fix warning missing handling of switch label
PdfEncodingLimits: Fixed warning on initialization order

PdfEncoding: Make the class final and non virtual

Also made PdfEncoding::ExportToFont() private/internal
PdfMemDocument: Fixed missing override attribute reset(), clear()

Cleanings: Make many classes final and constructors private (internal use)

Changes documented in https://github.com/podofo/podofo/wiki/PoDoFo-API-migration-guide (0.10 -> 0.11/1.0).
Moved PdfFilterFactory, PdfObjectStreamParser to private folder.
Cleanings: Make some more method internal and structs final
